---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="HPパッケージ選択｜和-Node" description="事業規模に合わせて選べる3つのホームページパッケージ。和-Node独自のプレミアム・カスタマイズをご提案します。">
  <!-- Luxury Background Layer -->
  <div class="luxury-bg">
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-3"></div>
    <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <main class="demos-page">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <header class="demos-header reveal">
        <div class="header-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">Select Your Grade</span>
          <h1>理想を形にする、<br/><span class="accent-text">3つのパッケージ案</span></h1>
          <p class="header-desc">事業の成長フェーズや目的に合わせて選べる、戦略的Webパッケージをご用意しました。最高級のデザインと最新技術を、あなたのビジネスの強力な武器に。</p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Package Selection Grid -->
      <div class="package-grid">
        <!-- Business 7 -->
        <article class="package-card reveal">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="package-tag">Standard Efficiency</div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <h2>Business 7</h2>
              <p class="price-label">¥150,000〜</p>
              <div class="divider"></div>
              <ul class="feature-list">
                <li><span>サイドメニュー（左側固定）</span></li>
                <li><span>基本7ページ構成</span></li>
                <li><span>プレミアム・フィニッシュ</span></li>
                <li><span>スマホ最適化（完全レスポンシブ）</span></li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/portfolio-lp/demo-business-7/index.html" class="demo-btn">デモを体験する</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Premium 10 -->
        <article class="package-card reveal featured">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="package-tag">Most Popular choice</div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <h2>Premium 10</h2>
              <p class="price-label">¥220,000〜</p>
              <div class="divider"></div>
              <ul class="feature-list">
                <li><span>フローティング・ガラスヘッダー</span></li>
                <li><span>心理導線10ページ構成</span></li>
                <li><span>SEO強化5セクション追加</span></li>
                <li><span>リッチアニメーション演出</span></li>
                <li><span>優先サポート対応</span></li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/portfolio-lp/demo-premium-10/index.html" class="demo-btn">デモを体験する</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Enterprise 15+ -->
        <article class="package-card reveal">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <div class="package-tag">High-End Performance</div>
            <div class="package-body">
              <h2>Enterprise 15+</h2>
              <p class="price-label">ASK</p>
              <div class="divider"></div>
              <ul class="feature-list">
                <li><span>全画面ドロワーメニュー</span></li>
                <li><span>15ページ超の包括的構成</span></li>
                <li><span>カスタムWebアプリ・DX連携</span></li>
                <li><span>採用・実績・ブログ全網羅</span></li>
                <li><span>独自DB・API連携対応</span></li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/portfolio-lp/demo-enterprise-15/index.html" class="demo-btn">デモを体験する</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Functional Comparison -->
      <section class="comparison-section reveal">
        <div class="glass-panel">
          <h2 class="sec-title">グレード別機能比較</h2>
          <div class="table-wrap">
            <table class="comparison-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>機能 / プラン</th>
                  <th>Business 7</th>
                  <th>Premium 10</th>
                  <th>Enterprise 15+</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>標準構成枚数</td>
                  <td>7枚</td>
                  <td>10枚</td>
                  <td>15枚〜</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>デザイングレード</td>
                  <td>High Quality</td>
                  <td>Luxury Glass</td>
                  <td>Ultimate Custom</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>アニメーション</td>
                  <td>標準</td>
                  <td>リッチ</td>
                  <td>フルカスタム</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>SEO対策</td>
                  <td>標準内部対策</td>
                  <td>戦略的セクション追加</td>
                  <td>全ページ完全最適化</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>システム連携</td>
                  <td>基本フォーム</td>
                  <td>基本フォーム</td>
                  <td>カスタムDB/API</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section class="demo-cta reveal">
        <div class="cta-inner">
          <h2>あなたのビジョンに、<br/>最適なプランを。</h2>
          <p>どのパッケージが最適か、専門のコンサルタントがアドバイスいたします。</p>
          <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScUbeK9em6cjegU5ha5Sh2fWamrIbxDuhmHDJPIN_no5Sj8-w/viewform" class="cta-primary-btn" target="_blank">無料相談を予約する</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Luxury Backdrop */
  .luxury-bg {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
    background: #0a0a0c;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .grid-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 50px 50px;
  }
  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(120px);
    opacity: 0.35;
    animation: orbFloat 25s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
  }
  .orb-1 { width: 700px; height: 700px; background: radial-gradient(circle, #2d4f1e 0%, transparent 70%); top: -20%; left: -10%; }
  .orb-2 { width: 600px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(circle, #1e3a5f 0%, transparent 70%); bottom: -10%; right: -5%; animation-delay: -7s; }
  .orb-3 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(circle, #4a3b1e 0%, transparent 70%); top: 40%; left: 30%; animation-delay: -12s; }

  @keyframes orbFloat {
    0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
    100% { transform: translate(60px, 40px) scale(1.1) rotate(15deg); }
  }

  .demos-page { padding-bottom: 120px; color: #fff; }
  .demos-header { padding: 140px 0 80px; text-align: center; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 900; color: #639922; letter-spacing: 0.4em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; display: block; }
  .demos-header h1 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .accent-text { color: #639922; text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.3); }
  .header-desc { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #aaa; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8; }

  /* Package Grid */
  .package-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 100px; align-items: stretch; }
  .package-card { position: relative; transition: 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1); }
  
  .card-inner {
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 40px;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .package-card:hover .card-inner {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(-15px);
  }

  .package-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 900; color: #639922; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .package-body h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .price-label { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: #639922; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .divider { width: 40px; height: 2px; background: #639922; margin-bottom: 40px; }

  .feature-list { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 60px; flex: 1; }
  .feature-list li { margin-bottom: 18px; color: #ccc; font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .feature-list li::before { content: "•"; color: #639922; font-size: 1.5rem; }

  .package-card.featured .card-inner {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.08) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 100%);
    border-color: rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.3);
  }
  .package-card.featured::after {
    content: "RECOMMENDED";
    position: absolute; top: -15px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: #639922; color: #fff; padding: 8px 24px; border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.15em; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.3);
  }

  .demo-btn {
    display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 22px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; transition: 0.4s;
  }
  .package-card.featured .demo-btn { background: #639922; border: none; }
  .demo-btn:hover { background: #fff; color: #000; transform: scale(1.03); }

  /* Comparison Section */
  .comparison-section { margin-top: 120px; }
  .glass-panel {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    backdrop-filter: blur(30px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 80px 60px;
  }
  .sec-title { text-align: center; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  .comparison-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; min-width: 800px; }
  .comparison-table th, .comparison-table td { padding: 28px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }
  .comparison-table th { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #639922; font-weight: 900; }
  .comparison-table td:first-child { text-align: left; color: #888; font-weight: 700; width: 250px; }

  /* CTA Section */
  .demo-cta { margin-top: 140px; text-align: center; }
  .cta-inner {
    padding: 100px 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 100%);
    border-radius: 60px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }
  .demo-cta h2 { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .demo-cta p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 50px; }
  .cta-primary-btn {
    display: inline-block; padding: 24px 70px; background: #fff; color: #000;
    text-decoration: none; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: 0.4s;
  }
  .cta-primary-btn:hover { background: #639922; color: #fff; transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(99, 153, 34, 0.3); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .package-grid { gap: 30px; }
    .package-card.featured { scale: 1; }
    .glass-panel { padding: 40px 20px; }
    .demo-cta h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
  }

  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: 1s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1); }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });

    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
